      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "If you enable only SCR wakeup in PMSWCR0 (Standby and Wake-up Control Register_, then Aurix can be started only when actual wakeup source is detected"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To make Aurix start on Power on Reset, make sure the below bit is set in PMSWCR0 register"
    },
